\FF[yuri_angry]Yurika: "That's the situation. We somehow managed to escape,
but the monster's control extends not only to our student
council... but also to the teachers..."

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "How did we manage to escape...? It lacked a bit of
realism, but..."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "If Akerunaru has already fallen into the enemy's
hands... it means this new monster is a super dangerous
opponent that even agents can't defeat."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "The problem is that it's very difficult to
distinguish between the monster and humans. Even I couldn't
see through the members of the student council or the
teachers who had fallen."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[syuu_smile]\AA[2]Hiiragi: "Yeah, that's the tricky part about Reverse Poison.
You can't tell if someone has fallen just by looking at
them."

\F[nako_true]\FF[syuu_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "What does that mean...? If you're talking about
the way they speak or dress like a gal, wouldn't that be
noticeable...?"

\F[nako_true]\FF[sumire_angry]\AA[2]Sumire: "That's what's so terrifying about Reverse Poison.
The appearance we see is just a 'front.' In reality, it's an
illusion for camouflage."

\F[nako_true]\FF[sumire_angry]\AA[2]Sumire: "They look no different from usual, going about
their daily lives. But their true nature..."

\F[nako_true]\FF[sumire_angry]\AA[2]Sumire: "...is transformed into an unbearable bitchy gal on
the 'inside.' I've experienced it myself, and it's certainly
something you'd want to hide. An appearance you can't
show..."

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[sumire_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "Illusion?... So you're saying the monster is an
illusionist?"

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[syuu_smile]\AA[2]Hiiragi: "Exactly. That's why you can't trust appearances or
actions. We have to defeat Amachi without falling for her
triggers..."
\F[nako_true]\FF[syuu_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "You two seem to know a lot about this monster."

\F[nako_true]\FF[syuu_smile]\AA[2]Hiiragi: "Like I said earlier, I'm the original identity of
that monster♪ Amachi is like a fan who awakened by taking me
as a reference♪"

\F[nako_true]\FF[sumire_trouble]\AA[2]Sumire: "In Hiiragi's case with Reverse Poison, the trigger
was cigarette smoke. When she inhaled the purple smoke, she
would feel good and..."
\F[nako_true]\FF[sumire_trouble]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "So... we need to be careful when it gets smoky?"
\F[beni_angry2]\FF[sumire_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "No... I think it's something else."
\F[beni_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "Why are you so sure...?"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "I'm concerned about what Amachi said, 'Look at me.'
I think there's a hint there."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Maybe it's something like getting hypnotized by
looking into her eyes... or some kind of mechanism where an
accessory she wears acts as a trigger..."
\F[beni_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "..."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[sumire_smile]\AA[2]Sumire: "I see. That makes sense. She was trying to recruit
the student council president as an ally, but she was doing
it gradually."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[syuu_smile]\AA[2]Hiiragi: "If she wanted to make us inhale cigarette smoke,
she would have come closer. It makes sense if she was trying
to show us 'something' of hers."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "As expected from the head of the detective club. It
was worth consulting with you."
\F[nako_smile]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Wow... Akane is being praised."

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "This is just basic reasoning... And Nadeshiko's
comment is kind of bothering me..."

\F[nako_true]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "So... what are you planning to do now? Are you
going to cooperate with us to stop Amachi?"

\F[nako_true]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "That's right. If possible, I'd like to do that. But
for now, I want to help as many people waiting for rescue as
I can."

\F[nako_true]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "Satsuki must be on guard knowing that we'll strike
back. We want to avoid further damage while she's on the
run..."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "So by helping them, you're making bait for Amachi to
come out..."
\F[nako_angry]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "!!"

\F[nako_angry]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "Exactly. This is the best strategy we can take
right now, Suzaku-san. It may sound harsh, but in this case,
charity is what will corner evil."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "I mean... I don't want to use helping people in that
way... I wish it could be more pure-hearted..."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "This is no time for idealism. Do you have any
better ideas?"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[syuu_smile]\AA[2]Hiiragi: "Now now, you two. Arguing here won't solve
anything. Besides... there's one big problem left, isn't
there?"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[sumire_trouble]\AA[2]Sumire: "Yes. Regardless, we can't proceed until we solve
that..."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[sumire_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "You mean a way to tell apart the monster from those
who are safe?"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[syuu_smile]\AA[2]Hiiragi: "Right! You're sharp!! This is a difficult feat.
Without an idea..."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[sumire_trouble]\AA[2]Sumire: "If only there were a way to discern them without
them realizing..."
\F[beni_angry2]\FF[sumire_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "..."
\F[beni_angry2]\FF[sumire_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "There's just one thing... that might work!"

\F[beni_angry2]Akane: "Inukai-sensei! You know the phone number for Taiyu-
sensei, the school nurse, right?"
Anna Maple: "!!"
Anna Maple: "Uh... yes..."
\FF[syuu_smile]Hiiragi: "!?"
\FF[sumire_trouble]Sumire: "Inukai-sensei is in such a place...!?"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[sumire_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "I want you to call her out!! With her ability... she
can search for people who are waiting for help!"

Anna Maple: "O-okay... then... I'm sorry, but... could you
take off your clothes?"
\F[beni_smile]Akane: "I understand. I'll wait for you to change."
\F[beni_smile]\FF[syuu_smile]\AA[2]Hiiragi: "Eh... what!? I'm really curious about this~♪"

\F[beni_smile]\FF[sumire_trouble]\AA[2]Sumire: "This might be... something we shouldn't pry
into..."

\FF[inu_smile]Anna Maple: "Yes. She said she'll come over. She also wants
to help the students..."
\FF[iruka_laugh]Iruka: "Phew... it's so hot with so many people around."
\F[beni_trouble]\FF[iruka_laugh]\AA[1]Akane: "..."
\F[nako_trouble]\FF[iruka_laugh]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "..."

\F[syuu_smile]\FF[iruka_laugh]\AA[1]Hiiragi: "No, if you're both crammed into a tight locker
getting cozy with each other"
\F[sumire_trouble]\FF[iruka_laugh]\AA[1]Sumire: "Hiiragi-san!"

\FF[yuri_smile]Yurika: "I can't believe Taiyu-sensei was also a monster.
And one with the purpose of helping people... how
intriguing."

\F[beni_smile]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Yes. She should definitely be able to tell them
apart."
\FF[syuu_smile]Hiiragi: "Suzukake-senpai... are you a lesbian?"
\F[iruka_trouble]\FF[syuu_smile]\AA[1]Iruka: "Eh? What do you mean...!"

\F[iruka_trouble]\FF[syuu_smile]\AA[2]Hiiragi: "Because you were getting cozy with the teacher,
right? The teacher's beautiful blonde hair... it's sticking
to your face♪"
\F[iruka_trouble]\FF[syuu_smile]\AA[1]Iruka: "Ahh... r-really..."

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[syuu_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "(It's like getting caught cheating... it really
happens... what will the seniors do?)"
\F[inu_trouble]\FF[syuu_smile]\AA[1]Anna Maple: "W-we like both. Girls and... boys..."

\F[inu_trouble]\FF[sumire_trouble]\AA[2]Sumire: "Please don't take Hiiragi-san seriously. And you
shouldn't say such things with a straight face, teacher..."
\F[beni_trouble]\FF[sumire_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "(Likes girls too...!? Inukai-sensei is...!!)"

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[syuu_laugh]\AA[2]Hiiragi: "That's right. Girls together can be nice too~♪ I
get it~♪ Akane-chan and Nadeshiko-chan look like a lovely
couple♪"
\F[nako_shy2]Nadeshiko: "Don't joke around... please."

\F[nako_shy2]\FF[syuu_laugh]\AA[2]Hiiragi: "Your face is red, Nadeshiko-chan. Could it be...
you've imagined it~. Kissing Akane-chan♪"
\F[nako_shy2]\FF[syuu_laugh]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "I am not..."

\F[beni_shy2]Akane: "(Nadeshiko isn't denying it...!? Could it be... she
wants to kiss me!?)"
\F[beni_ero]Akane: "(Guhh...♪ I can't stand this...♪)"

\F[beni_ero]Akane: "(I can't stop fantasizing... I need to go to the
bathroom right now to let it out...)"
\F[beni_ero]Akane: "(But I know this isn't the time for that...)"
